data.description: Welcome to 1940 Suzanne Street! This great home offers the perfect blend of convenience and comfort on charming Johns Island with the added benefit of no HOA! After entering you will immediately notice the bamboo flooring, which beautifully complements the abundant natural light throughout the entire first floor. The kitchen boasts recently installed appliances, all of which have been upgraded within the last two years. Each of the secondary bedrooms are located upstairs along with the primary suite complete with double sinks in the bathroom and a generously sized walk-in closet. The rear patio area is an oasis, providing an ideal space to unwind and enjoy the fully fenced backyard. Check out all that this lovely home has to offer today!
